data.description: Introducing your dream home in the serene countryside! Nestled amidst the picturesque charm of rural living, this all-brick exterior home offers you the ideal lifestyle you've always desired. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, it's the perfect retreat for those seeking peace and tranquility without the constraints of an HOA. Sitting on a generous 1.26-acre lot, this property is your canvas to create your own outdoor oasis. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the seamless blend of modernity and comfort. The kitchen boasts sleek, soft-close cabinetry and features stainless appliances from trusted brands such as Frigidaire, Samsung, and Whirlpool, ensuring that your culinary adventures are a breeze. The quality engineered flooring and elegant granite countertops in both the kitchen and bathrooms add a touch of luxury to your daily life. Keeping your comfort in mind, a new Waldrop HVAC system ensures year-round climate control. As the evening draws near, gather around the stone fireplace with a wood mantle, adorned with inviting gas logs, and enjoy cozy nights with loved ones. Ceiling fans throughout the home provide a gentle breeze, enhancing your relaxation. For those who appreciate the outdoors, a spacious deck at the rear of the home invites you to soak in the natural beauty of the surroundings. The Solar Eclipse energy-efficient solar panel system not only reduces your energy costs but also showcases your commitment to a sustainable lifestyle. This property is perfectly practical too, with a paved multi-car driveway and the option for the qualified buyer to possibly assume the owner's 3% +/- mortgage, making your transition into this dream home even smoother. Convenience is key - while the property provides an escape from the hustle and bustle, it's still just a stone's throw away from shopping, restaurants, and schools. With easy access to Interstates #26 and #85, you can effortlessly connect with all that the area has to offer. Discover the perfect blend of country living and modern comfort in this home. Make your move and embrace the lifestyle you've always longed for. This is more than just a house; it's the beginning of a new chapter in your life. Welcome home.
